22 A BINARIO (10110)

22 / 2 = 11     [0]↑
11 / 2 = 5      [1]↑
5  / 2 = 2      [1]↑
2  / 2  = 1     [0]↑
1  / 2  = 0     [1]↑  


15 A BINARIO (1111)

15 / 2 = 7 [1]↑
7  / 2 = 3 [1]↑
3  / 2 = 1 [1]↑
1  / 2 = 0 [1]↑


